Hey, so this is a submission to the OnTheHub Network Student Essentials contest! I don't know if the number of likes will come into play at all, but you should like it anyways! So, here's a little background to the things in front of you. 
A Minolta XG-1 - Because it's old and broken and awesome. 
Guitar picks and a capo - When I need some music. 
An iPod and headphones - When I need a more talented source of music. 
Sunglasses - Because of the Sun, right? 
My wallet - To remind myself that I'm broke. (Go Tigers) 
My watch - Time, duh. 
Vans - Because I look damn good in them. 
Ghost Chili Hot Sauce - Because hot sauce is the nectar of the Gods. 
My Phone - so I can talk with all you beautiful people. 
Cheers
